<br>
Ten of the souls caught on fire, and since they were already nice'n'dry they went of in flames in a snap. Thanatos did a large circle around the main area of fighting taking off many heads with his sword. He looked around him and saw that there were more of the living dead coming out of the crevaces in the cavern.* <br>
