*Thanatos suddenly spotted a rather large figure coming through a opening in the cave. A Troll that had died three years ago, by the sword of a young hero in Southern Greece... Thanatos's sword suddenly became on fire and surged with power that it absorbed from the underworld around it. He than threw the sword as it flew almost as fast as Hermes and hit the troll in the chest igniting his body in an explosion of fire from within him.<br>
