*By now the souls were pouring out of the of the openings unstoppable, and Thanatos's reserve warriror were getting few in number. Thanatos had also grown plenty more pissed about the whole situation. Thanatos had seemed to have grown a little bigger and looked plenty more like death itself. His cloak was dusty and had lots of tear marks in it it. Thanatos had turned his morphing weapon into his big wickedly curved sythe. <br>
